Package: soovee-core
Architecture: all
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Depends: soovee-lib, python-eyed3, pyxdg, ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: SooVee Serial Audio Manager - Core
 SooVee Serial Audio Manager for a serial audio service feed subscriptions like 
 on Podiobooks. This package contains the core soovee components.

Package: soovee-lib
Architecture: all
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: SooVee Serial Audio Manager - Library
 SooVee Serial Audio Manager for a serial audio service feed subscriptions like 
 on Podiobooks. This package contains the reuseable components from soovee.
 
